+        // [GIVEN] A raw item with unit cost 100
+        // [GIVEN] A finished goods item with indirect cost 10% and a production BOM with 1 unit of the raw item
+        // [GIVEN] A production order with two lines for the FG item, qty 10 each (total 20)
